# Python Command-line Options Map

Small and simple library that handle both command line parsing
and configuration reading from a file.

The only thing you have to do, is to describe options and parameters
your main function expects, throught a YAML resource file.

## Installation

Via pypi, setuptools or pip (source code available at github :
https://github.com/Aygos/python-com.git).

